metadata.name: RADIANT
metadata.description:
Radiant is an original artwork created using Oil/ Acrylic paint mediums
The intending idea of radiant is to create a painting that portrays positivity and happiness
How it radiates on us
How we're able to light up dark places being who we are and how that positive radiation can be transferred to our surrounding
Being RADIANT is about embracing ones own divinity, and i believe that if we're able to do that, we can rise above negativity and shine like radiant beings that we are.
We have a choice
